---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'FWMAV',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="relative h-[70vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden -mt-[80px] pt-[80px]">
    <video 
      src="/portfolio/fwmav_background.mov" 
      autoplay loop muted playsinline 
      class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover -z-10"
    ></video>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 -z-10"></div>
    
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white tracking-wide text-center font-heading drop-shadow-lg px-4">
      Flapping-Wing Micro Air Vehicle
    </h1>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading border-b-2 border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-800 pb-4">
      FWMAV Beta Subteam
    </h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-10">
      The objective of FWMAV's Beta subteam was to create a drone that uses a bio-inspired flapping wing design for propulsion. Using SolidWorks, 3D printing, laser cutting, and lots of testing, I helped to make Beta fly.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <img src="/portfolio/fwmav_team_photo.HEIC" alt="Beta Team" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700" />
      <img src="/portfolio/beta_flight.gif" alt="Beta Flight GIF" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700" />
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl my-6 border border-gray-100 dark:border-gray-800">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading">Design</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-12">
      My specific role on FWMAV was to design, manufacture, and test components to improve Beta's design. This included major revisions to the flapping mechanism and flapping components to decrease mass and increase reliability. My main focus was on the design of the chassis, which acts as the motor mount and gear hub for the flapping mechanism. This component was one of the heaviest on the drone, and its main structure as well as mounting system to the drone frame left a large room for improvement in terms of reducing mass. I designed, 3D printed, and tested many iterations of the chassis before settling on the final design that was both light enough and strong enough for Beta to fly. The efforts of my team and I reduced the mass of the drone by 19%, while increasing thrust by four times, enabling flight.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="/portfolio/mechanism_1.png" alt="Mechanism View 1" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3" />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">Initial chassis mechanism mount</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="/portfolio/mechanism_2.png" alt="Mechanism View 2" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3" />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">Initial chassis design</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="/portfolio/mechanism_3.png" alt="Mechanism View 3" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3" />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">Finalized chassis design with updated mounting</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="/portfolio/beta_assembly_1.jpg" alt="Beta 1.0 Assembly" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3" />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">Initial Beta drone assembly (~310 grams)</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="/portfolio/beta_assembly_2.jpg" alt="Beta 2.0 Assembly" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3" />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">Final Beta drone assembly (~252 grams)</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="/portfolio/rocker_1.png" alt="Rocker 1" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3" />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">Initial rocker design</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="/portfolio/rocker_2.png" alt="Rocker 2" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3" />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">Final rocker design strengthened to avoid failure at high flapping frequencies</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>

    <figure class="flex flex-col items-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <img src="/portfolio/mechanism_top.png" alt="Mechanism Top View" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3" />
      <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">Beta flapping mechanism diagram</figcaption>
    </figure>

    <figure class="flex flex-col items-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <video 
        src="/portfolio/mechanism_assembly_demo.mp4" 
        class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"
        autoplay loop muted playsinline controls
      ></video>
      <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">
        Beta flapping mechanism
      </figcaption>
    </figure>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 mb-20">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 font-heading">Failures</h2>
    <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-12">
      There were many failures on the path to Beta's ultimate success. One of the major issues faced by the team was mechanism reliability, as the flapping frequency of 30 hertz would shred gears and break printed plastic components. I redesigned the chassis to maximize strength while minimizing weight. Another major problem was slippage of the main gear shaft that would cause the mechanism to fall out of alignment, dropping the thrust to near zero. I came up with the solution to use a D-shaft, which eliminated all slippage, increasing reliability and thrust.
    </p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="/portfolio/shredded_gear.png" alt="Shredded gear" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3" />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">A shredded pinion gear</figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <video 
          src="/portfolio/flight_failure.mov" 
          class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3"
          autoplay loop muted playsinline controls
        ></video>
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">
          One of the many failures faced during testing
        </figcaption>
      </figure>
      <figure class="flex flex-col items-center">
        <img src="/portfolio/beta_thrust_test.gif" alt="Beta Thrust Test" class="w-full h-auto rounded-xl shadow-md border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-3" />
        <figcaption class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 text-center italic px-2">Mechanism thrust test</figcaption>
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
